{"tid":93650,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁既朋友應唔應該理番佢","createTime":"2017-01-24T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T05:29:18.000Z","uid":17554,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30ae6cdb47e99ca883c9770e6662fc039b5f5fc4","tid":93650,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"我以前平時都好關心佢 噓寒問暖唔少得 佢病無藥食都會拎俾佢 之前都成日一齊出街 都算best fd<br />\n<br />\n但平時鬧交佢都會當我出氣袋咁鬧 講啲說話好毒 有次仲話到我頂唔順喊左出嚟<br />\n<br />\n仲有因爲我以前讀書比佢好 我成日去佢屋企玩 佢阿媽就會拎我同佢嚟比較 所以我都覺好似間接hurt到佢<br />\n<br />\n咁我有次頂唔順佢啲脾氣就打算唔再理佢 順便希望少啲見面等佢唔洗聽佢阿媽講佢咁多 初頭大家都冷戰 但佢之後都死死氣搵番我 但feel唔到佢有悔意<br />\nA <br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該理番佢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好理"},{"pid":"52dedcbdf1c2a054df9c255c02bad11b4798a3b8","tid":93650,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"你女人嚟㗎？"},{"pid":"f47f5319712d3bf727272ca6ae5cf22c23b9a618","tid":93650,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你女人嚟㗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講野真喺唔留情面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鬧到我好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試諗下你親既人周不時當你沙包打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edc06c4f4c48b301f9ab5f73b869a7ff20e6d86","tid":93650,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你女人嚟㗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講野真喺唔留情面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鬧到我好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma